OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMost places will remain dry
OL,6,Fwith large amounts of cloud, although
OL,7,Fsome sunny intervals will develop,
OL,8,Fespecially this afternoon. Breezy
OL,9,Falong the coast, with a chance of
OL,10,Fisolated light showers. Warmer inland
OL,11,Fwith lighter winds. Temperatures close
OL,12,Fto average.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClear spells and patchy
OL,15,Fcloud, with a chance of a few light
OL,16,Fshowers reaching coastal areas, where
OL,17,Fit will remain breezy. Becoming cooler
OL,18,Ffor many places, compared to recent
OL,19,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
